high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the television.
Pick up the leftmost remote off of the table in front of you.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left to face the foot stool.
Put the remote on the foot stool to the right of the laptop.
Turn left and walk over to the television.
Pick up the remote off of the table in front of you.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to face the foot stool.
Put the remote on the foot stool above the keys.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to a foot stool.

high_descs: walk straight to face the left edge of the tv and tv stand
pick up the remote on the left from the tv stand
turn around, walk to face the ottoman with the laptop computer on it
put the remote on the ottoman to the right of the laptop computer
turn left, walk to face left side of tv and tv stand
pick up remote from tv stand
turn right, walk to face ottoman with laptop computer
place remote on laptop computer track pad and ottoman
anns.task_desc: put two remotes on an ottoman

high_descs: Walk ahead to the TV stand.
Pick up the remote on the left of the other remote.
Turn around and walk to the front of the ottoman.
Place the remote on the ottoman on top of the keys.
Turn left and walk back to the TV stand.
Pick up the other remote.
Turn around and walk to the front of the ottoman.
Place the remote behind the keys and slightly on top of the laptop track pad.
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on an ottoman.
